HEADWORD: Straightway
<hw>Straight"way`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>Immediately;
without loss of time; without delay.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>He took the damsel by the hand, and said unto her, Talitha cumi. .
